<p class="indent0" style="-uslm-lc:I11" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">For purposes of this title, if an organization is a private foundation (within the meaning of subsection (a)) on <date date="1969-10-09">October 9, 1969</date>, or becomes a private foundation on any subsequent date, such organization shall be treated as a private foundation for all periods after <date date="1969-10-09">October 9, 1969</date>, or after such subsequent date, unless its status as such is terminated under section 507.</p>
